<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 09:15:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>孟买办事处设立后中方敦促印方慎重处理台湾问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-india-handle-taiwan-issue-cautiously-after-mumbai-office-opening-2024-10-17/</link><description>中国周四敦促印度谨慎处理台湾问题，避免干扰台湾在孟买设立事实上的领事馆后的中印关系改善。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 08:56:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-india-handle-taiwan-issue-cautiously-after-mumbai-office-opening-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>攀登过世界 14 座最高峰的青少年表示，尼泊尔的夏尔巴人应该得到更多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepals-sherpas-deserve-more-says-teenager-who-scaled-worlds-14-tallest-peaks-2024-10-17/</link><description>一名尼泊尔青少年是有史以来登顶世界所有 14 座最高峰的最年轻的人，他表示希望利用自己的技能造福喜马拉雅山国家的夏尔巴社区，并培养出世界级的运动员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 08:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepals-sherpas-deserve-more-says-teenager-who-scaled-worlds-14-tallest-peaks-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>由于美元走强，投资者转空大多数亚洲外汇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/investors-turn-short-most-asian-fx-dollar-strength-prevails-2024-10-17/</link><description>分析师转而看空大多数亚洲货币，对印度卢比的空头押注创一年新高，因预期美联储降息幅度较小，美元走强，并削弱了风险较高的亚洲资产的光芒。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 07:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/investors-turn-short-most-asian-fx-dollar-strength-prevails-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国问题拖累保乐力加第一季度销售额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-woes-drag-down-pernod-ricard-first-quarter-sales-2024-10-17/</link><description>法国烈酒制造商保乐力加表示，尽管其第一季度销售额降幅超出预期，部分原因是中国市场疲软，但仍预计 2024/25 财年销售额将恢复增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 07:41:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-woes-drag-down-pernod-ricard-first-quarter-sales-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>台积电Q3利润大涨54% 好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q3-profit-rises-54-better-than-forecasts-2024-10-17/</link><description>台湾芯片制造商台积电周四公布第三季度净利润增长 54%，超出市场预期，因为该公司继续从人工智能应用中使用的半导体需求激增中获益。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 05:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q3-profit-rises-54-better-than-forecasts-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国问题拖累保乐力加第一季度销售额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-woes-drag-down-pernod-ricards-q1-sales-2024-10-17/</link><description>法国烈酒制造商保乐力加表示，尽管其第一季度销售额下降了 5.9%，低于预期（部分原因是中国市场疲软），但仍预计 2024/25 财年将恢复销售增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 05:32:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-woes-drag-down-pernod-ricards-q1-sales-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>迅达第三季度销量因新安装量减少和中国疲软而小幅下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-third-quarter-sales-slightly-fall-lower-new-installations-2024-10-17/</link><description>瑞士电梯和自动扶梯制造商迅达周四报告称，由于新安装量下降（主要是在中国），第三季度销售额下降 0.9%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 04:44:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-third-quarter-sales-slightly-fall-lower-new-installations-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，麦肯锡中国业务裁员数百人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/mckinsey-cuts-hundreds-jobs-china-business-wsj-reports-2024-10-17/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周三报道，美国咨询公司麦肯锡在减少与政府相关的客户并裁员约 500 人（约占其中国员工总数的三分之一）后，正在重组其中国业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 03:54:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/mckinsey-cuts-hundreds-jobs-china-business-wsj-reports-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>台湾高级官员称，中国正在建设快速打击台湾的能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-building-capacity-rapidly-strike-taiwan-senior-taiwanese-official-says-2024-10-17/</link><description>台湾一名高级安全官员表示，中国正在建设迅速将军事演习转变为全面攻击的能力，并提供了台北政府对北京本周在台湾进行的军演背后的战略意图的评估。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 03:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-building-capacity-rapidly-strike-taiwan-senior-taiwanese-official-says-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>Bajaj Auto 的节日销售警告加剧印度股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-shares-set-open-slightly-higher-earnings-focus-2024-10-17/</link><description>印度股市周四下跌，原因是摩托车制造商 Bajaj Auto 对节日季销售疲软的警告波及整个行业，加剧了高股票估值和外国资金外流的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 02:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-shares-set-open-slightly-higher-earnings-focus-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国增加住房项目资金以支持陷入困境的行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expand-financing-housing-projects-4-trln-yuan-says-housing-minister-2024-10-17/</link><description>中国住房和城乡建设部部长倪虹周四表示，中国将扩大符合融资条件的住房项目“白名单”，并在年底前将此类开发项目的银行贷款增加至4万亿元人民币（5620亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 02:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expand-financing-housing-projects-4-trln-yuan-says-housing-minister-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市上涨，欧元在欧洲央行之前疲软，“特朗普贸易”提振美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-17/</link><description>周四，在欧洲央行预期降息之前，欧元跌至 11 周低点，而欧洲股市则小幅上涨，平衡了华尔街股市的涨幅和亚洲股市的跌幅，其中中国的住房政策简报表现平平。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 01:54:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>日本石破向靖国神社供奉祭品激怒中韩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-ishiba-sends-offering-yasukuni-shrine-ahead-election-2024-10-17/</link><description>日本首相石破茂办公室周四表示，他向东京靖国神社献上了祭品，此举引起了韩国和中国的批评，两国认为靖国神社是日本军国主义过去的象征。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 01:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-ishiba-sends-offering-yasukuni-shrine-ahead-election-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行降息前欧元触及数周低点；美元坚守“特朗普贸易”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-11-week-high-eyes-china-property-briefing-2024-10-17/</link><description>在欧洲央行预计降息之前，欧元周四跌至两个多月低点，而美元则触及 11 周以来的最高水平，市场认为特朗普的政策更为乐观，他将赢得美国大选。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 00:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-11-week-high-eyes-china-property-briefing-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国称日本渔船“非法”进入领海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-japanese-fishing-boat-illegally-entered-territorial-2024-10-17/</link><description>中国海警称，10月15日至16日，一艘日本渔船“非法进入”中国钓鱼岛领海，并被警告驱离。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 00:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-japanese-fishing-boat-illegally-entered-territorial-2024-10-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>